@startuml 07-mgr-latency
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

title MGR Write Latency - Paxos Overhead

participant "Client" as client
participant "Node 1\n(Primary)" as node1
participant "Node 2" as node2
participant "Node 3" as node3

client -> node1 : INSERT INTO orders...
activate node1

node1 -> node1 : Prepare TX
node1 -> node2 : Broadcast TX
node1 -> node3 : Broadcast TX

node2 -> node2 : Certify TX
node2 --> node1 : ACK

node3 -> node3 : Certify TX
node3 --> node1 : ACK

note over node1
  **Wait for Majority (2/3)**
  LAN: +0.5ms ~ +2ms
  WAN: +100ms ~ +300ms
end note

node1 -> node1 : COMMIT
node1 --> client : OK
deactivate node1

note bottom
  **The Physics Problem:**
  Singapore <-> New York: ~200ms RTT
  Every write waits for consensus
  TPS drops dramatically over WAN
end note

@enduml
